data.description:
This tastefully updated home offers a perfect blend of modern features and cozy comforts. Step inside and be greeted by the beautifully updated interior. The kitchen is a true gem, boasting butcher block countertops, elegant white cabinets, and a matching backsplash with stainless steel appliances that add sophistication to this culinary haven.Experience the ease of maintenance with tile and vinyl flooring throughout, creating a seamless flow and stress-free routine. The main floor houses a spacious master bedroom featuring a modern ensuite bathroom and a beautifully tiled shower, creating a luxurious retreat to unwind after a long day.Upstairs, find two additional bedrooms with ample space and natural light. The large loft is thoughtfully designed with a built-in desk and shelving, perfect for a productive home office or cozy reading nook.
Entertain guests in style in the generously sized backyard with an expansive covered patio, ideal for BBQs or relaxed evenings under the stars. The landscaped low-maintenance vegetation adds to the surroundings, simplifying outdoor enjoyment.
Convenience is key, with proximity to Senita Valley Elementary and Civano Community School for an easy commute. Direct access to I-10 ensures seamless journeys to your destination. Schedule a showing today and experience the charm and comfort of this Southeast Tucson dream home.
